<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.3.10">
<l>veṉṟa tolcīrt teṉṉi laṅkai veñcamat taṉṟarakkar</l>
<l>kuṉṟa maṉṉā rāṭi yuynta kuḻama ṇitūrattai</l>
<l>kaṉṟi neynnīr niṉṟa vēṟkaik kaliya ṉolimālai</l>
<l>yoṉṟu moṉṟu maintum mūṉṟum pāṭi niṉṟāṭumiṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Dance and keep singing these one-and-one-and-five-and three [verses]</l>
<l>Of the garland of words by Kaliyaṉ, a vicious spear in hand</l>
<l rend="indent">where wet blood lingers,</l>
<l>About the kuḻamaṇitūram by which the demons, dancing like mountains,</l>
<l rend="indent">were saved</l>
<l>That day on the heated battlefield in Laṅkā of the South,</l>
<l rend="indent">its ancient fame defeated.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
